Hello there !
Quick question, are the weekly calls still running and where can the info on how to join be found ?
THanks

The NetCDF/HDF5/geospatial calls stopped in July 2023 because the grant ended. You can find notes in a folder on Google Drive, linked from a mailing list post.

There's a new grant/project with a geospatial component but I'm not especially involved and I'm not sure about meetings.
